data.description: This one-story home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a flex room suitable for a children's retreat, home office or formal dining room. The spacious, chef-ready kitchen is equipped with a full suite of Whirlpool brand kitchen appliances, granite countertops and gorgeous wood cabinets. A beautiful bay window in the breakfast room overlooks the front yard landscaping. The owner’s retreat showcases a luxurious bathroom, large walk-in closet, and access to the back yard.
